{"word":"Kingdom of Heaven","slug":"kingdom-of-heaven","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Kingdom of Heaven</b> Likened to:<br/> - A man who sowed good seed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=30'>Mat 13:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=43'>Mat 13:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=29'>Mar 4:29</a> <br/> - A grain of mustard seed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=32'>Mat 13:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=31'>Mar 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=19'>Luk 13:19</a> <br/> - Leaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=33'>Mat 13:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=21'>Luk 13:21</a> <br/> - A treasure<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=44'>Mat 13:44</a> <br/> - A pearl<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=45'>Mat 13:45</a> <br/> - A net<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=50'>Mat 13:50</a> <br/> - A king who called his servants to a reckoning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=35'>Mat 18:35</a> <br/> - A householder<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=20&verse=16'>Mat 20:16</a> <br/> - A king who made a marriage feast for his son<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=14'>Mat 22:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=24'>Luk 14:24</a> <br/> - Ten virgins<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=13'>Mat 25:13</a> <br/> - A man traveling into a far country, who called his servants, and delivered to them his goods<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=30'>Mat 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=19&verse=27'>Luk 19:27</a> <br/> &#187;My kingdom is not of this world&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=36'>Joh 18:36</a><br/> Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=3'>Mat 18:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=14'>Mat 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=14'>Mar 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=16'>Luk 18:16</a><br/> Rich cannot enter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=24'>Mat 19:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=25'>Mar 10:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=25'>Luk 18:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=30'>Luk 18:30</a><br/> Keys of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=19'>Mat 16:19</a><br/> Glad tidings of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=1'>Luk 8:1</a><br/> Mysteries of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=10'>Luk 8:10</a><br/> Is not meat and drink<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=14&verse=17'>Rom 14:17</a><br/><a href='S:Church (1)'>Church (1)</a>; <a href='S:Jesus, The Christ, Kingdom of'>Jesus, The Christ, Kingdom of</a>"}]}